data.description: Prime location to town and walking distance to Edgerton elementary school, nice neighborhood and the generous .48 acre corner lot makes this two-story home featuring an oversized 2-car garage your perfect home. This 2,256 square foot home offers two spacious living rooms, a sizable laundry room, and an office. The main bedroom is currently located in the lower level for added privacy. Enjoy the large fenced yard and back deck. Don't miss the extra potential in the substantial bonus area between the laundry and garage, complete with a separate entrance. This property offers versatile living options for your ideal lifestyle. Call Alice Brotnov at 406-229-0120, or your real estate professional.
